[Name] Slim
[Summary] Desktop-independent graphical login manager
[Description]  SLiM is a Desktop-independent graphical login manager for X11, derived from Login.app. It aims to be light and simple, although completely configurable through themes and an option file; is suitable for machines on which remote login functionalities are not needed.
